\s Wachunga walilinda
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Wachunga walilinda kundi lao kwa usiku\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Tazama, malaika aliwatokea mbio, Kutoka kwake \bd*\bd Mungu\bd*\bd .\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Na utukufu wake Bwana ukawaangazia\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Wakaogopa sana wakiona nuru ile, Wakashutuka kweli.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Na malaika yake Bwana akawaambia\bd*\bd :\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd “\bd*\bd Musiogope, kwani ninawaletea ninyi Habari toka \bd*\bd Mungu\bd*\bd .\bd*\bd ”\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd “\bd*\bd Habari Njema ya furaha itakayokuwa Kwa watu wote wa dunia, ninaleta kwenu Habari Njema hii.\bd*\bd ”\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd “\bd*\bd Kwa maana mutajua leo tu amezaliwa Katika muji wa Daudi kwa ajili yenu Mwokozi Kristo Bwana.\bd*\bd ”\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd “\bd*\bd Na hii alama kwenu mutamwona kwa kizizi, Amelalishwa kwa sanduku ya kulisha nyama\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Mutamukuta pale.\bd*\bd ”\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Kwa gaf\bd*\bd ’\bd*\bd la makutano ya majeshi ya\bd*\bd  Mbingu\bd*\bd ni Walizunguka huyu malaika yake Bwana, Na\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd walisifu \bd*\bd Mungu\bd*\bd .\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd “\bd*\bd Ee utukufu kwake \bd*\bd Mungu\bd*\bd , kule kwa\bd*\bd  Mbingu\bd*\bd ni\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Salama duniani kwa wanaomupendeza\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Ee, sifa kwake \bd*\bd Mungu\bd*\bd .\bd*\bd ”\bd*
